version_description:
- Refunds made easy! use your ASDA app to start refunds right from your phone.
- Bug fixes and improvements

- Reviews are back! Sorry it took so long for us to squash that big bug.
- It's frustrating when items are out of stock. To make it a little easier, tap the "See Alternatives" button to see suggestions for out of stock items

New and improved Delivery Pass with added customer benefits:
• Delivery Pass Dashboard in My Account
• Ability to book recurring slots
• Easy auto renewal
• and more to come...

- Redesigned home screen

Thank you for using ASDA's mobile app! To improve the app for you, our team releases regular updates to make it smoother... better... and faster. Browse our shop today and book a delivery or collection time that suits you!

- Bug fixes

Thank you for using ASDA's mobile app! To improve the app for you, our team releases regular updates to make it smoother... better... and faster. Browse our shop today and book a delivery or collection time that suits you!

- Save time on your next pick up! New Click & Collect Mobile Check-in lets you to notify us when you’re on your way to pick your order so it’s ready when you arrive. Get the latest version of the app to see if your nearest ASDA store supports Check-in now.
- Security enhancements and bug fixes.

Improved messaging for order status to reduce your wait times and make your collections more convenient.
Security enhancements and bug fixes.
Security enhancements and bug fixes

- Improved order amends to make it easier to add and remove items from upcoming orders.
- Added pricing information for products even before they become available, so you can make informed decisions and save money.
- Added more nutrition information and highlighted allergens for products to enable you to make more informed shopping decisions.
- Security enhancements and bug fixes.

- Improved order amends to make it easier to add and remove items from upcoming orders.
- Added pricing information for products even before they become available, so you can make informed decisions and save money.
- Added more nutrition information and highlighted allergens for products to enable you to make more informed shopping decisions.
- Security enhancements and bug fixes.
We've redesigned the order details screen to make it clearer to understand the status of your order and its contents.
- We've added hi-res images to our product details screen with zoom functionality so you can view items up close
Bug fixes and enhancements
- We've added hi-res images to our product details screen with zoom functionality so you can view items up close
- We've added hi-res images to our product details screen with zoom functionality so you can view items up close

-Before you go:
We've made improvements to the before you go section to ensure you never forget your favorite items.
-Refund Status Updates:
Finding out your Refund Status is easier then before. No need to call Contact Centre. Now visit Order Details Page to track the progress of your refund.
-More Info Link
Now customers can get more information around why their order may have Failed Authorization. Just click on More Info link in Order Details Page.
